==English==

===Noun Phrase===
'''busted flush'''

# {{poker}} A potential [[flush]] which ultimately was not [[fill]]ed.
#: ''I thought I'd draw another spade, but I ended up with a busted flush.''
# {{idiom}} Anything which ends up worthless despite great potential.

